- wmaker crashes if a parse error occurs
- the animation of shade puts ImageMagick in a weird state
- during startup, transient windows should be miniaturized with their owners
  not in their own icons
- in focus follow mouse mode with autoraise, it is possible to
  put window raising in a endless loop.
- shaped windows don't resize very well
- AutoArrangeIcons=NO will not work correctly if StickyIcons is enabled
